*Jedemo* (We are eating) salatu za ručak.
(We are eating salad for lunch.)

Deca *jedu* (They are eating) sladoleda.
(They are eating ice cream.)

Ona će *jesti* (She will eat) pileću čorbu.
(She will eat chicken soup.)

Mi smo *jeli* (We had eaten) sendviče.
(We had eaten sandwiches.)

Oni *jedosmo* (We had eaten) pre neki dan.
(We had eaten the other day.)